# Original-form capture produces large binaries (WARC, HTML, PDF, PNG).
# Per CAPTURE-RUNBOOK.md these live in off-platform custody; only the small
# integrity records are tracked in-repo so the chain is auditable without GBs.
*/original/*
!*/original/manifest.json
!*/original/sha256sums.txt
!*/original/archive-org-snapshots.txt
